<div id="ftn1" style="mso-element: footnote">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 6pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify"><a title="" style="mso-footnote-id: ftn1" href="#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-language: RU; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">[1]</span></span></span></span></span></a><font size="2"><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"> Dussauge, P., Garrette, B</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">.</span><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"> Cooperative Strategy: Competing Successfully Through Strategic Alliances. &#8211; </span><st1:place><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">Chichester</span></st1:place><span lang="EN-GB" style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">, Wiley, 1999.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p></div>
<div id="ftn2" style="mso-element: footnote">
